cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.CL, cs.CV 

The paper discusses the problem of efficient retrieval of multimedia stimuli with annotated semantics and emotion, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR), multimedia (cs.MM), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), natural language processing (cs.CL), and computer vision (cs.CV). The study involves evaluating the influence of keywords and dimensional emotions in manual retrieval of pictures, which further supports the relevance of these sub-categories.
